title Séquence : Demandeur - Accéder et Modifier les Corrections

actor "Demandeur" as Demandeur
participant "Register\n(Page)" as RegisterPage
participant "useRegistration\n(Hook)" as RegHook
participant "RegistrationService" as Service
participant "RegistrationRepository" as Repository
participant "Cloud Function\nverifySecurityCode" as CloudFunction
participant "Cloud Function\nsubmitCorrections" as CloudFunction2
database "Firestore\n(membership-requests)" as Firestore

== Phase 1 : Accès via URL ==

Demandeur -> RegisterPage: Accéder à /register?requestId=XXX
activate RegisterPage

RegisterPage -> RegHook: useRegistration() initialisé
activate RegHook

RegHook -> RegHook: Extraire requestId depuis URL

alt requestId présent
  RegHook -> Repository: getById(requestId)
  activate Repository

  Repository -> Firestore: getDoc(membership-requests, requestId)
  activate Firestore
  Firestore --> Repository: DocumentSnapshot
  deactivate Firestore

  alt Demande OK (under_review + securityCode)
    Repository --> RegHook: MembershipRequest
    deactivate Repository

    RegHook -> RegHook: Vérifier securityCodeUsed
    alt Code déjà utilisé
      RegHook -> RegisterPage: Afficher erreur "Code déjà utilisé"
      RegHook -> RegisterPage: setIsCacheLoaded(true)
      deactivate RegHook
      deactivate RegisterPage
    else Code non utilisé
      RegHook -> RegHook: Vérifier expiration (expiry < now)
      alt Code expiré
        RegHook -> RegisterPage: Afficher erreur "Code expiré"
        RegHook -> RegisterPage: setIsCacheLoaded(true)
        deactivate RegHook
        deactivate RegisterPage
      else Code valide
        RegHook -> RegHook: Créer correctionRequest (isVerified=false)
        RegHook -> RegisterPage: setCorrectionRequest(correctionRequest)
        RegHook -> RegisterPage: setIsCacheLoaded(true)
        RegisterPage -> RegisterPage: Afficher banner + formulaire code
      end
    end

  else Demande invalide / sans corrections
    Repository --> RegHook: null
    deactivate Repository
    RegHook -> RegisterPage: Afficher formulaire normal
    RegHook -> RegisterPage: setIsCacheLoaded(true)
  end

else Pas de requestId
  RegHook -> RegisterPage: Afficher formulaire normal
  RegHook -> RegisterPage: setIsCacheLoaded(true)
end

deactivate RegHook

== Phase 2 : Vérification du Code de Sécurité ==

Demandeur -> RegisterPage: Saisir code (6 chiffres)
Demandeur -> RegisterPage: Cliquer "Vérifier le code"
activate RegisterPage

RegisterPage -> RegHook: verifySecurityCode()
activate RegHook

RegHook -> RegHook: Valider format (6 chiffres)

alt Format invalide
  RegHook -> RegisterPage: Afficher erreur "Code invalide"
  deactivate RegHook
  deactivate RegisterPage
else Format valide
  RegHook -> Service: verifySecurityCode(requestId, code)
  activate Service

  Service -> Service: Appel Cloud Function\nverifySecurityCode(requestId, code)
  activate Service

  Service -> CloudFunction: httpsCallable('verifySecurityCode')\n{ requestId, code }
  activate CloudFunction

  note right of CloudFunction
    **Cloud Function :**
    - Transaction atomique Firestore
    - Vérifie code, expiration, usage
    - Marque comme vérifié (securityCodeVerifiedAt)
    - Retourne isValid + requestData
  end note

  CloudFunction -> Firestore: runTransaction()\nVérification atomique
  activate Firestore
  Firestore --> CloudFunction: { isValid, requestData? }
  deactivate Firestore

  CloudFunction --> Service: { isValid: boolean, reason?: string, requestData?: {...} }
  deactivate CloudFunction

  Service --> RegHook: { isValid, reason?, requestData? }
  deactivate Service

  alt Code valide (isValid === true)
    RegHook -> Service: loadRegistrationForCorrection(requestId)
    activate Service

    Service -> Repository: getById(requestId)
    activate Repository

    Repository -> Firestore: getDoc(membership-requests, requestId)
    activate Firestore
    Firestore --> Repository: MembershipRequest
    deactivate Firestore

    Repository --> Service: MembershipRequest
    deactivate Repository

    Service --> RegHook: RegisterFormData
    deactivate Service

    RegHook -> RegHook: isVerified=true + reset(formData) + resetSteps()
    RegHook -> RegisterPage: Afficher formulaire pré-rempli
    RegHook -> RegisterPage: Masquer formulaire code + afficher toast succès
  else Code invalide (isValid === false)
    alt reason === 'CODE_INCORRECT'
      RegHook -> RegisterPage: Afficher erreur "Code incorrect"
    else reason === 'CODE_EXPIRED'
      RegHook -> RegisterPage: Afficher erreur "Code expiré"
    else reason === 'CODE_ALREADY_USED'
      RegHook -> RegisterPage: Afficher erreur "Code déjà utilisé"
    else reason === 'REQUEST_NOT_FOUND'
      RegHook -> RegisterPage: Afficher erreur "Demande introuvable"
    else
      RegHook -> RegisterPage: Afficher erreur "Code invalide"
    end
  end

  deactivate RegHook
  deactivate RegisterPage
end

== Phase 3 : Modification des Données ==

Demandeur -> RegisterPage: Modifier champs selon reviewNote
loop Pour chaque étape du formulaire
  Demandeur -> RegisterPage: Valider étape
  RegisterPage -> Service: validateStep(step, formData)
  activate Service
  Service --> RegisterPage: StepValidationResult
  deactivate Service
end

== Phase 4 : Soumission des Corrections ==

Demandeur -> RegisterPage: Soumettre formulaire
activate RegisterPage

RegisterPage -> RegHook: submitForm()
activate RegHook

RegHook -> Service: updateRegistration(requestId, formData, code)
activate Service

Service -> Service: Appel Cloud Function\nsubmitCorrections(requestId, code, formData)
activate Service

Service -> CloudFunction: httpsCallable('submitCorrections')\n{ requestId, code, formData }
activate CloudFunction

note right of CloudFunction
  **Cloud Function :**
  - Transaction atomique Firestore
  - Vérifie code, expiration, usage
  - Marque code comme utilisé (securityCodeUsed = true)
  - Met à jour données + statut = 'pending'
  - Nettoie champs correction (securityCode, reviewNote, etc.)
  - Garantit atomicité (tout ou rien)
end note

CloudFunction -> Firestore: runTransaction()\nMise à jour atomique
activate Firestore
Firestore --> CloudFunction: { success: boolean }
deactivate Firestore

CloudFunction --> Service: { success: boolean, error?: string }
deactivate CloudFunction

Service --> RegHook: { success: boolean, error?: string }
deactivate Service

alt Succès (success === true)
  RegHook -> RegisterPage: Toast succès + page confirmation
else Erreur (success === false)
  alt error === 'CODE_INCORRECT'
    RegHook -> RegisterPage: Afficher erreur "Code incorrect"
  else error === 'CODE_EXPIRED'
    RegHook -> RegisterPage: Afficher erreur "Code expiré"
  else error === 'CODE_ALREADY_USED'
    RegHook -> RegisterPage: Afficher erreur "Code déjà utilisé"
  else error === 'REQUEST_NOT_FOUND'
    RegHook -> RegisterPage: Afficher erreur "Demande introuvable"
  else
    RegHook -> RegisterPage: Afficher erreur "Erreur lors de la soumission"
  end
end

deactivate RegHook
deactivate RegisterPage

note over Firestore
  **Transaction atomique garantit :**
  - Statut = 'pending'
  - securityCodeUsed = true
  - securityCode = null (nettoyé)
  - reviewNote = null (nettoyé)
  - securityCodeExpiry = null (nettoyé)
  - Données mises à jour
  - Pas de race condition possible
end note

@enduml


